      "factId": "hz.web.1bb646c219940f02.fact.3",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "This is a web project and online arts community that celebrates homepages, virtual worlds, the world-wide-web and the digital lives that all netizins share, here at the dawn of the digital age.",
