      "charStart": 399,
      "factId": "hz.web.1bb646c219940f02.fact.4",
      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "This project has three goals: To make the web; genuine, chaotic, timeless, individual and joyful To provide knowledge and support to humans creating digital worlds To promote websites and digital worlds as mediums of visual art MelonLand is part of a wider movement sometimes called the web revival ; to join, all you need to do is choose to engage with small handmade web projects next time you're online!",
